Description: Kneu Health, based in London, innovates in the healthcare sector by transforming smartphones into clinical-grade monitors for neurological conditions, focusing initially on Parkinson's and dementia. This approach not only empowers individuals living with such conditions but also aids clinicians in offering personalized care and helps healthcare systems reduce pressure while enhancing patient outcomes.
Name: Kneu Health

Description: Dealstack is the operating system for private equity, providing a comprehensive platform that manages private capital operations effectively. Key offerings include fund management, corporate structures management, compliance automation, and operational efficiency tools, catering to private equity firms that require precision and efficiency amidst evolving industry demands. Dealstack is trusted by leading private capital sponsors worldwide, aiming to facilitate smoother investment processes through innovative technology.

Description: Treble Peak is a digital gateway to Europe's leading private equity and venture capital funds, established to expand investment potential without the usual barriers to entry. Name: Treble Peak

Description: Jenesys AI is a London-based company focused on AI-powered bookkeeping automation for the UK accounting sector, founded in 2023.
